	<TITLE></TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY LANG="en-US" DIR="LTR">
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><I>Description:</I></P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm">Manager asks the employee for overtime
work. The employee accepts or declines the proposal. After that the
manager receives the notification of acceptance or rejection.</P>
<P LANG="ru-RU" STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><I>How to play the business process:</I></P>
<OL>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm">Log in as member of manager group
	(e.g. julius)</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm">Click menu item &ldquo;Process
	Definitions&rdquo; 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm">Click &ldquo;Start&rdquo; for 
	&ldquo;over time work demo&rdquo; button</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><FONT SIZE=3>Start form will
	appear. </FONT>
	</P>
</OL>
<UL>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm">Choose an employee,
	which will receive proposal for an overtime work (e.g. Gaiua)</P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><SPAN LANG="en-US"><FONT SIZE=3>Enter
	the time interval for the overtime work (e.g. 14.03.2006 22:30 -
	20</FONT></SPAN>.12.2005 23:30)</P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><FONT SIZE=3>Fill the
	fields  &laquo;reason&raquo; and &laquo;comment&raquo;</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><FONT SIZE=3>Click &ldquo;OK&rdquo;</FONT></P>
</UL>
<P STYLE="margin-left: 2.5cm; margin-bottom: 0cm">The new instance of
&ldquo;over time work demo&rdquo; business process will be created
and the employee (gaiua) will receive task.</P>
<OL START=5>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><FONT SIZE=3>Click
	&ldquo;Logout&rdquo;</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"> <FONT SIZE=3>Log in as
	employee, selected on the start form (gaiua). </FONT>
	</P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><FONT SIZE=3>Click the
	&ldquo;make a decision&rdquo; task.</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><FONT SIZE=3>Choose
	&ldquo;accept&rdquo; or  &ldquo;decline&rdquo; (e.g. &ldquo;accept&rdquo;),
	fill the &laquo;comment&raquo; field and click &laquo;OK&raquo;.</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><FONT SIZE=3>Logout </FONT>
	</P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><FONT SIZE=3>Log in as
	the actor, which started the process (<FONT FACE="Arial CYR, sans-serif">julius</FONT>)</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><FONT SIZE=3>Click on
	task &ldquo;Notify for acceptance&rdquo;.</FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><FONT SIZE=3>By
	clicking &ldquo;OK&rdquo; you&rsquo;ll finish the process.</FONT></P>
</OL>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><BR>
</P>
<P STYLE="margin-left: 1.91cm; text-indent: -1.91cm; margin-bottom: 0cm">
<I>Note</I>. To monitor process click on &ldquo;Process Instances&rdquo;
menu item and then click on instance.</P>
<P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0cm"><I>Note</I>. To see the business
process graph click on &ldquo;Process Definitions&rdquo; menu item
and click on process properties.</P>
</BODY>
</HTML>